# Storyblok Components

This project integrates with Storyblok as a headless CMS. Components in Storyblok correspond to Astro components in the codebase.

## Component Mapping

The mapping between Storyblok components and Astro components is defined in [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs).

## Main Components

- Layout Components:
  - [Page.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Page.astro) - Main page container
  - [Grid.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Grid.astro) - Grid layout component
  - [Row.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Row.astro) - Row layout component

- Content Components:
  - [Hero.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Hero.astro) - Hero section
  - [Text.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Text.astro) - Text block component
  - [Card/](mdc:src/storyblok/Card) - Card component
  - [List.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/List.astro) - List component
  
- Interactive Components:
  - [Button.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Button.astro) - Button component
  - [Link.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Link.astro) - Link component
  - [Accordion.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Accordion.astro) - Accordion component
  - [Form/](mdc:src/storyblok/Form) - Form components
  - [Input.astro](mdc:src/storyblok/Input.astro) - Input field component
  
## Type Generation

Storyblok component types can be generated using:
```
npm run storyblok:generate-types
```

This updates the TypeScript definitions in [src/types/component-types-sb.d.ts](mdc:src/types/component-types-sb.d.ts)
